[[File:XT8-Challenge66.png|thumb|right|XT-8, a modified XT droid]]
The '''XT labor droid''' was a stocky, barrel-chested [[Droid/Legends|droid]] with strong arms which hung to its knees. It was produced around [[20,000 BBY/Legends|20,000 BBY]] and, though its personality matrix was crude by the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], it was high technology when it was first produced. One such droid, [[XT-8]], had been modified to become an [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]].

